# libfwbpi - Firmware Bank Programming Interface

A C library for dual-bank firmware updates on embedded systems.

## Features

- Dual-bank (A/B) firmware update support
- WIC image handling and partition management
- MD5 verification for integrity checking
- Progress callbacks for status monitoring
- Clean C API with comprehensive error handling

## Building

```bash
# Build library and examples
make

# Build debug version
make debug

# Run tests
make check

# Install system-wide
sudo make install
```

## Quick Start

```c
#include <libfwbpi.h>

int main() {
    fwbpi_init(NULL);
    fwbpi_result_t result = fwbpi_update_firmware("http://server/firmware.wic.bz2");
    fwbpi_cleanup();
    return (result == FWBPI_SUCCESS) ? 0 : 1;
}
```

## Documentation

See `docs/` directory for detailed API documentation and examples.

